a6deea4ac596acbc09a35b36bb17fe5b8937f","tid":351454,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160707/mobile/bkn-20160707180434015-0707_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160707%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20160707180434015-0707_00862_001.html&d=wf4GiX5tyj8uccFk1MzqeP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=30980c43\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160707/mobile/bkn-20160707180434015-0707_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">ViuTV選美二十強 趙詠瑤認有整容</span><br />\n2016年07月07日(四)<br />\n<br />\nViuTV選美節目《美選D.n.A》舉行二十強見面會。網絡女神的張沛樂（沙律）順利入圍，而已婚又整過容的趙詠瑤亦有入圍。<br />\n<br />\n趙詠瑤從事過醫學美容，亦承認自己整過容，她說：「整過眼同鼻，同自體脂肪隆胸，眼係吊線，鼻係用耳骨！」她表示當時是因為工作關係，所以願意整容，現在就覺得足夠，未有需要再整。<br />\n<br />\n問到可會擔心整容影響評判觀感？趙詠瑤說：「唔太誇張就OK，之前自體隆胸依家都冇晒，因為減肥都會減埋！」上月27日結婚的她，表示老公亦有前來支持，又自爆曾出寫真，但未有用誇張手法去宣傳故沒有太大回響。"},{"pid":"663817b9728238046ee431c2b11f9e046b159202","tid":351454,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2More奴已經覺得好正<br />\n不過整容</blockquote><br />\n我都係2more奴開始j<br />\n<br />\n佢地啲片都幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cff5bb5f2018b9da47de65d0438a2662f5b9cc6","tid":351454,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2More奴已經覺得好正<br />\n不過整容</blockquote><br />\n我都係2more奴開始j<br />\n<br />\n佢地啲片都幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇個的士片幾搞笑"},{"pid":"76bf27fb3e8a05e224cd6bd24e6b1c0d2619cda1","tid":351454,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"b9856ba2a1fa1ada5f0e992edd71ec3cb3652376","tid":351454,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:36:53